{"tid":947453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地鐵 十月四綫齊冧事故, 只罰 800萬","createTime":"2018-12-19T09:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T10:47:46.000Z","uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b22787d4d978ce18bef753fc7fd273ad3be08ab8","tid":947453,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T09:31:07.000Z","msg":"爆到咁大鑊, 都係罰 800萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港鐵提交調查報告交代10月16日早上荃灣綫、港島綫、觀塘綫及將軍澳綫的四綫事故，報告指出是由於兩個供應商的信號系統，軟件計數器重置互不協調，一個需要自動重置，一個要人手重置。<br />\n<br />\n當日事故發生時啟動了重置，由於4條綫互相聯繫，令區間電腦重複執行重置動作，出現不穩定狀況，而車務及維修人員從未知悉系統軟件重置運算方法，以及對列車服務的影響。<br />\n<br />\n報告建議在軟件數據達到重置啟動點或上限數値前，以人手重置系統內的計數器，並成立專責小組，就未來新建及須改動的關鍵系統，加强整合，以及檢討調派接駁巴士行走受影響主要港鐵站。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵車務總監劉天成形容事故前所未見，並再次向受影響乘客致歉，<span style=\"color: red;\">由於涉及4條綫，當作4宗事故，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每宗罰款200萬元，共罰款800萬元</span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1434071-20181219.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1434071-20181219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4GjDEg7Vel6eijA17OryLCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c220165e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1434071-20181219.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=223000ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1434071-20181219.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"53d9fcce1ccc8e01614d8a87f99d76501fb2a81b","tid":947453,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T09:32:41.000Z","msg":"左手罰右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2e6bd3b1cf4350de50d323804c54040b1f08f3","tid":947453,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T09:32:57.000Z","msg":